<br>
I do agree with much of what you said though.<br>
<br>
If I were to completely lose my mind and leave the League and decide to apply to, say, the Tinker's Pride (if it still existed), I would expect a certain level of opposition.  No matter how I roleplay - I'm a dark elf!  I can roleplay a gnomish pirate, I can pretend to tinker, but really ... 'purists' will always doubt my gnomishness.  <br>
<br>
